Overview
========

**opensubtitles-dl** downloads and unpacks subtitles from
https://www.opensubtitles.org/:

.. code:: console

   $ ls -1 night-of-the-living-dead.*
   night-of-the-living-dead.mp4

   $ opensubtitles-dl --help
   Usage: opensubtitles-dl FILE URL

   $ opensubtitles-dl night-of-the-living-dead.mp4 https://www.opensubtitles.org/en/subtitles/4025513/night-of-the-living-dead-en
   https://dl.opensubtitles.org/en/download/sub/4025513 -> night-of-the-living-dead.srt

   $ ls -1 night-of-the-living-dead.*
   night-of-the-living-dead.mp4
   night-of-the-living-dead.srt

   $ grep -B1 "They're coming to" night-of-the-living-dead.srt
   00:06:10,852 --> 00:06:14,117
   They're coming to get you, Barbra.

Prerequisites
=============

* bash
* curl (â‰¥ 7.18.2)
* UnZip_

.. _UnZip:
   https://infozip.sourceforge.net/UnZip.html

